OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772787895
OL,3,CLabour MP Joani Reid 'voluntarily'
OL,4,Csuspends herself over China spy
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FScottish Labour MP, Joani Reid, said
OL,8,Fshe has "voluntarily" suspended
OL,9,Fherself from the Labour whip "until
OL,10,Finternal investigations are concluded"
OL,11,Fafter her husband was arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of spying for China.
OL,14,FDavid Taylor, Reid's husband, and two
OL,15,Fother men were arrested by counter-
OL,16,Fterrorism officers at addresses in
OL,17,FLondon and Wales on Wednesday.
OL,26,@pD@IOUpD@UO]qD@^OUrD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
