PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772787895
OL,3,CLabour MP Joani Reid 'voluntarily'
OL,4,Csuspends herself over China spy
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FTaylor is a lobbyist and the director
OL,8,Fof a PR, communications and
OL,9,Fconsultancy business called Earthcott
OL,10,FLimited.
OL,12,FHe is also the director of policy and
OL,13,Fprogrammes at Asia House, which is a
OL,14,FLondon-based think tank aiming to
OL,15,Fstrengthen economic ties between Asia,
OL,16,Fthe Middle East, and Europe.
OL,18,FTaylor is accused of assisting a
OL,19,Fforeign intelligence service.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
