PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772787895
OL,3,CLabour MP Joani Reid 'voluntarily'
OL,4,Csuspends herself over China spy
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FReid herself is not accused of
OL,8,Fwrongdoing.
OL,10,FIt comes as US legislators hit out at
OL,11,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,12,Fgovernment after the arrest of three
OL,13,Fmen, including Reid's husband, on
OL,14,Fsuspicion of spying for Beijing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
