PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772787895
OL,3,CLabour MP Joani Reid 'voluntarily'
OL,4,Csuspends herself over China spy
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FUS Representative John Moolenaar, the
OL,8,FHouse select committee on the Chinese
OL,9,FCommunist Party's chairman, cited the
OL,10,Fdecision to greenlight plans for a new
OL,11,FLondon mega embassy and the collapse
OL,12,Fof a case against two alleged Chinese
OL,13,Fspies last year as having emboldened
OL,14,FBeijing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772787895
OL,3,CLabour MP Joani Reid 'voluntarily'
OL,4,Csuspends herself over China spy
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FMoolenaar said in a statement
OL,8,Faddressing the arrests: "The British
OL,9,FGovernment's failure to properly
OL,10,Fprosecute alleged spies last (autumn),
OL,11,Fcoupled with its approval of China's
OL,12,Fmega embassy, only emboldens the CCP's
OL,13,F(Chinese Communist Party) espionage
OL,14,Factivities in the UK.
OL,16,F"As one of our closest security
OL,17,Fpartners with access to American
OL,18,Fintelligence on China, the UK's
OL,19,Fcommitment to protecting sensitive
OL,20,Finformation must be beyond doubt.
OL,26,@pD@YOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772787895
OL,3,CLabour MP Joani Reid 'voluntarily'
OL,4,Csuspends herself over China spy
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"These cases should be prosecuted
OL,8,Fthoroughly, and the UK should rescind
OL,9,Fits approval of the mega embassy."
OL,11,FResponding at the time to her
OL,12,Fhusband's arrest, Joani Reid said: "I
OL,13,Fhave never been to China. I have never
OL,14,Fspoken on China or China-related
OL,15,Fmatters in the Commons. I have never
OL,16,Fasked a question on China-related
OL,17,Fmatters.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@bO]tD@dOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772787895
OL,3,CLabour MP Joani Reid 'voluntarily'
OL,4,Csuspends herself over China spy
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"As far as I am aware, I have never
OL,8,Fmet any Chinese businesses whilst I
OL,9,Fhave been an MP, any Chinese diplomats
OL,10,For government employees, nor raised
OL,11,Fany concern with ministers or anyone
OL,12,Felse on behalf of, even
OL,13,Fcoincidentally, Chinese interests."
OL,15,FShe added: "I am not any sort of
OL,16,Fadmirer or apologist for the Chinese
OL,17,FCommunist Party's dictatorship.
OL,19,F"I have never seen anything to make me
OL,20,Fsuspect my husband has broken any law."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@cO]wD@LOU{D@AOU|D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
