CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772787895
OL,3,CLabour MP Joani Reid 'voluntarily'
OL,4,Csuspends herself over China spy
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FCommander Helen Flanagan, head of
OL,8,FCounter Terrorism Policing London,
OL,9,Fpreviously said the force does not
OL,10,Fbelieve there to be "any imminent or
OL,11,Fdirect threat" related to the arrests.
OL,13,FTaylor was arrested in London, a 43-
OL,14,Fyear-old man was arrested in Pontyclun
OL,15,Fin South Wales, and a 68-year-old was
OL,16,Farrested in the county of Powys in mid-
OL,17,FWales, with all three being detained
OL,18,Funder the Police and Criminal Evidence
OL,19,FAct.
OL,26,@rD@UOUsD@NO]
